A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering neon-lit skyscrapers are constructed from interconnected geometric modules and blocks, each module glowing with different colored circuit patterns in electric blue, magenta, and orange. The buildings are linked by luminous data streams flowing between them like bridges of light. In the foreground, a massive holographic gear mechanism floats above the street, its transparent teeth interlocking with smaller mechanical components scattered across multiple floating platforms at different heights. Rain falls through volumetric light beams, creating reflections on wet chrome surfaces below. The architecture combines organic curves with sharp industrial angles, suggesting both harmony and complex interdependence between the structures.
